<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your Business Name</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Fast, reliable garage door repair services. Call now for same-day service.">

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      background: #111;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .cta-btn {
      background: #ff6600;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .hero {
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581578731548-c64695cc6952') no-repeat center/cover;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 100px 20px;
    }

    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 40px 20px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .services {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .reviews {
      background: #f4f4f4;
    }

    footer {
      background: #111;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>Your Business Name</h1>
  <a href="tel:1234567890" class="cta-btn">Call Now</a>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <h2>Fast & Reliable Garage Door Repair</h2>
  <p>Same-day service. Affordable pricing. Trusted locally.</p>
  <a href="tel:1234567890" class="cta-btn">Get a Free Quote</a>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Our Services</h2>
  <div class="services">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Garage Door Repair</h3>
      <p>Broken springs, cables, rollers, and more.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>New Door Installation</h3>
      <p>Upgrade your home with a brand new garage door.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Emergency Service</h3>
      <p>24/7 fast response when you need it most.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section reviews">
  <h2>What Customers Say</h2>
  <p>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ “Fast, professional, and affordable. Highly recommend!”</p>
  <p>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ “Showed up same day and fixed everything.”</p>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>📞 Call: <a href="tel:1234567890">123-456-7890</a></p>
  <p>📍 Serving your local area</p>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Your Business Name</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
